-- Portsmouth Sale is Concluded Allowing Soccer Club to Exit Administration
-- B y   M i k e   H a r r i s o n
-- 2010-10-24T06:16:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-24/portsmouth-sale-is-concluded-allowing-soccer-club-to-exit-administration.html
Portsmouth City soccer club’s
administrators said talks between various parties concerning the
sale of the club have been “satisfactorily concluded.”   “The club has now been formally sold and will continue to
trade outside of administration,” a statement on the club’s
website said today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
